EASTERN NORTH ATLANTIC. OUTER HEBRIDES WESTWARDS. CHART GB 1128.
1. LIVE WEAPONS FIRING IN PROGRESS DAILY BETWEEN 0800 AND 1800 UTC 12
TO 16 SEP WITHIN CIRCULAR AREA RADIUS 32 MILES CENTRED ON 57-26N 009-09W.
